145
00:12:57,025 --> 00:12:59,334
The way he watches you...

146
00:12:59,334 --> 00:13:00,865
It's like he's willing to leap
in front of you,

147
00:13:00,865 --> 00:13:02,934
and take a bullet
or something.

148
00:13:03,779 --> 00:13:05,366
Is that a bad thing?

149
00:13:06,254 --> 00:13:08,766
It's an intense thing.

150
00:13:08,766 --> 00:13:10,482
You're different with him.

151
00:13:11,851 --> 00:13:15,455
If he moves, you move.
Like magnets.

152
00:13:16,966 --> 00:13:19,317
I don't know, we're  just...

153
