In love.
I get it.

154
00:13:22,823 --> 00:13:23,638
I just want to make sure,

155
00:13:23,638 --> 00:13:26,176
you're making
the right choices for you.

156
00:13:27,549 --> 00:13:29,905
You know, cause you're the one
who's gonna have to live with him.

157
00:13:33,721 --> 00:13:36,719
