163
00:14:09,983 --> 00:14:12,317
To keep you warm up in Alaska.

164
00:14:13,071 --> 00:14:16,150
Remember this one?
Ensanada.

165
00:14:16,150 --> 00:14:17,850
- The snake pit.
- Yep.

166
00:14:18,798 --> 00:14:20,789
But this one is my favourite.
Here...

167
00:14:21,628 --> 00:14:24,127
The three-headed lobster
in Maine.

168
00:14:24,127 --> 00:14:26,793
- This is amazing.
- No, honey. I'm glad you've like it.

169
00:14:26,793 --> 00:14:28,900
I just figured, you know,
when you get older, have kids,

170
00:14:28,900 --> 00:14:30,352
We can add to it.
Maybe go visit...

171
00:14:30,352 --> 00:14:32,667
the world's largest catsup bottle
or something.

172
00:14:32,667 --> 00:14:34,673
- Thanks
- Oh...

173
