I'm glad you like it.

174
00:14:38,878 --> 00:14:42,826
I just thought, you should have
a little piece of me, up there in Alaska.

175
00:14:44,896 --> 00:14:47,217
- Mom.
- Yeah.

176
00:14:50,591 --> 00:14:55,858
- I miss you.
- Oh, honey. I miss you too.

177
00:15:13,149 --> 00:15:15,248
You sure this is
where you saw her?

178
00:15:16,287 --> 00:15:18,266
She's almost here.

179
00:15:31,052 --> 00:15:32,315
On your left!

180
00:16:08,023 --> 00:16:11,165
Wait!
She's in their territory.

181
00:16:12,682 --> 00:16:14,355
She'll get away!

182
00:16:15,606 --> 00:16:17,130
No she won't!

183
00:16:52,755 --> 00:16:54,419
Emmett, no!

184
00:17:27,272 --> 00:17:28,879
Did you regret going?

185
00:17:30,739 --> 00:17:32,020
No.

186
00:17:33,338 --> 00:17:37,954
It was really great to see my mom.
Just really hard saying goodbye.

187
00:17:38,870 --> 00:17:42,703
- It doesn't have to be goodbye.
- Is that why you ask me to go?

188
00:17:43,280 --> 00:17:45,347
You thought
I was gonna change my mind.

189
00:17:46,792 --> 00:17:49,084
I'm always hoping for that.

190
00:17:50,679 --> 00:17:51,981
What?

191
00:17:53,269 --> 00:17:56,203
If I asked you to stay in the car,
would you?

192
00:18:02,578 --> 00:18:04,059
Of course not.

193
00:18:16,322 --> 00:18:17,362
Hey.

194
00:18:18,822 --> 00:18:22,834
- Charlie said you left town.
- Yeah. To visit my Mom, why?

195
00:18:23,635 --> 00:18:25,645
Just checking to see
if you're still human.

196
