223
00:20:17,666 --> 00:20:20,275
- Look who's back.
- Whatup, Bella?

224
00:20:20,275 --> 00:20:23,994
- Quil, you too?
- Yep. Finally made the pack.

225
00:20:23,994 --> 00:20:25,071
I'm glad you're here, Bella.

226
00:20:25,071 --> 00:20:27,745
Maybe we can get a break from
Jake's obsessive inner monologue.

227
00:20:27,745 --> 00:20:29,331
"I wish Bella would call".

228
00:20:29,431 --> 00:20:31,965
- "I wish Bella wouldn't call".
- "Maybe I should call Bella".

229
00:20:31,965 --> 00:20:34,088
"Maybe I should call Bella
and hang up".

230
00:20:35,102 --> 00:20:37,037
Alright, you can shut up now.

231
00:20:39,940 --> 00:20:43,508
Bella, this is Leah Clearwater.
Harry's daughter.

232
00:20:44,113 --> 00:20:47,367
Hey.
I'm really sorry about your father.

233
00:20:47,367 --> 00:20:50,373
If you're here to torture Jacob
some more, feel free to leave.

234
00:20:53,715 --> 00:20:55,429
Fun, isn't she?

235
00:20:56,030 --> 00:20:58,982
- Bella... Hi.
- Hey.

236
00:20:58,982 --> 00:21:01,738
I was wondering when we'd see
your face around here again.

237
00:21:01,738 --> 00:21:03,679
Yeah, same here.

238
00:21:03,679 --> 00:21:05,012
Sam, we're good?

239
00:21:05,012 --> 00:21:08,229
We're good. She won't be getting
through our line anytime soon.

240
00:21:19,555 --> 00:21:22,332
So, when did Leah
joined the pack?

241
00:21:22,332 --> 00:21:26,915
Around when her Dad died.
Her brother Seth, also phased.

242
00:21:26,915 --> 00:21:31,044
