but he's chomping at the bit.

244
00:21:35,378 --> 00:21:37,247
Wish it was Leah
who'd stay home.

245
00:21:38,169 --> 00:21:39,695
Come on,
don't be such a guy.

246
00:21:40,391 --> 00:21:46,291
No, it's... It's not a chick thing.
It's... You know, a triangle thing.

247
